    <detaileddescription>
<para>Thread colors that are subject to change are loaded at runtime, allowing us to update them as they change.</para>
<para>However, in-builts that use indicies like the DXF, SVG or HUS tables are compiled in. This should help with embedded compatibility in both cases. </para>
